# Pasadena Guide

The CurationsLA Christmas and Holiday Guide to Pasadena

Historic charm, parade traditions and elegant holiday displays.

Pasadena blends Victorian architecture and cultural institutions with long-running traditions like the Rose Parade season festivities and tree-lighting celebrations.

## Eat

Pasadena’s restaurants offer festive prix-fixe dinners around Old Town and near the Norton Simon; bakeries present seasonal confections and teas.

## Do

Explore tree lightings, holiday concerts and Pasadena’s seasonal museum programs; nearby Rose Bowl events extend the festive calendar.

## Stay

Historic hotels and boutique stays in Old Town provide classic holiday ambiance and proximity to events.

## Shop

Old Town Pasadena’s boutiques and Paseo Colorado host pop-ups and local markets for handcrafted gifts.

## Takeaway

Pasadena offers elegant holiday traditions, historic settings and cultural programming for a refined seasonal visit.

